thread.title: Jan & Fay
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Jan & Fay

author: Jan & Fay
title: Jan & Fay
text:
We couldn't have been happier with the level of service, advice etc that we received the Flemington office of Nelson Alexander. Everything was completed without any fuss or bother & in a very professional manner. To be able to buy & sell with the same people was a real bonus- the total package!
The experience was above our expectations & we couldn't have asked for anything more.
We would recommend Jayson, Josh & Kate to anyone interested in buying or selling.
